<h1>
  👋 {@user.name} wants you to join them on MOSSLET - social media that actually respects your privacy 🌿
</h1>

<p>
  Great news!
  <EmailComponents.highlight color="teal">
    <strong>{@user.name}</strong>
  </EmailComponents.highlight>
  has invited you to join them on MOSSLET – social media that actually respects your privacy and peace of mind. 🌱
</p>

<%= if @invitation.message not in ["", nil]  do %>
  <EmailComponents.gap />

  <h2>Personal Message from {@user.name}</h2>
  <EmailComponents.dotted_gray_box>
    <p class="align-center" style="font-style: italic; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
      "{@invitation.message}"
    </p>
  </EmailComponents.dotted_gray_box>
<% end %>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>
  Ready to experience social media without the stress, tracking, and manipulation? Click below to create your account and join {@user.name}:
</p>

<EmailComponents.button_centered to={@url} color="teal" size="lg">
  Join {@user.name} on MOSSLET
</EmailComponents.button_centered>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="success">
  <strong>🎉 What makes MOSSLET different:</strong>
  No ads, no tracking, no algorithms, no manipulation – just authentic connections with the people you care about.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.gray_box>
  <h3>🔗 Quick Steps to Connect with {@user.name}:</h3>

  <ol style="margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
    <li>Create your account using the button above</li>
    <li>Verify your email address</li>
    <li>Choose your lifetime plan (one-time payment)</li>
    <li>Find {@user.name} using their details:</li>
    <ul style="margin: 8px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {@user.email}</li>
      <li><strong>Username:</strong> @{@user.username}</li>
    </ul>
    <li>Send them a connection request</li>
    <li>Start enjoying private, peaceful social media! 🌿</li>
  </ol>
</EmailComponents.gray_box>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<h2>🌿 Why People Choose MOSSLET</h2>

<p>
  Tired of feeling anxious every time you open social media? You're not alone. MOSSLET was built for people who want to stay connected without the mental health toll.
</p>

<div style="display: grid; gap: 16px; margin: 24px 0;">
  <div style="padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #F0FDFA, #ECFDF5); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #10B981;">
    <strong>🔒 Privacy First:</strong>
    Your data stays yours. No selling, no tracking, no surveillance capitalism.
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #EFF6FF, #DBEAFE); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;">
    <strong>🧘 Calm by Design:</strong>
    No algorithmic manipulation, no endless scrolling, no anxiety-inducing features.
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #FAF5FF, #F3E8FF); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #8B5CF6;">
    <strong>💬 Real Connections:</strong>
    End-to-end encrypted messaging and genuine conversations with people you choose.
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 16px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, #FFFBEB, #FEF3C7); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;">
    <strong>🌱 Own Your Experience:</strong>
    You control what you see, share, and how you engage. Delete everything anytime.
  </div>
</div>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.accent_line width="60%" />

<h3>💰 Why One-Time Payment?</h3>

<p>
  Unlike "free" platforms that make money by exploiting your data and attention, MOSSLET uses a simple one-time payment model. This means:
</p>

<ul style="line-height: 1.6;">
  <li>
    <strong>You're the customer, not the product</strong>
    – we serve your interests, not advertisers
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>No hidden costs</strong> – pay once, use forever, no subscriptions or surprise fees
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Sustainable and honest</strong>
    – we can focus on building great features instead of maximizing engagement
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Community over profit</strong>
    – our success depends on your satisfaction, not your data
  </li>
</ul>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="info">
  <strong>💡 Did you know?</strong>
  The average person's data is worth about $700/year to companies like Facebook and Google. With MOSSLET, that value stays with you.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <h3>🛡️ Don't Know {@user.name}?</h3>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you don't recognize {@user.name} or didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email. No action is required.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    You can also create an account without connecting to them – they won't be notified unless you choose to send a connection request.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
